<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 02:29:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联盟针锋相对地否决了赋予以色列发布限制令的广泛权力的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/coalition-tit-for-tat-nixes-bill-giving-israel-sweeping-powers-to-issue-restraining-orders/00000191-242b-d19b-a3b7-b67fc6400000</link><description>拟议的法律将赋予地方法院权力，禁止公民离开家、使用互联网或到以色列境外旅行</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/coalition-tit-for-tat-nixes-bill-giving-israel-sweeping-powers-to-issue-restraining-orders/00000191-242b-d19b-a3b7-b67fc6400000</guid></item><item><title>真主党对以色列的威胁目前超过了伊朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-threat-on-israel-currently-outweighs-irans/00000191-2405-dc0c-a395-ae376d8d0000</link><description>来自黎巴嫩的袭击可能会以前所未有的强度针对以色列北部和中部的军事和战略地点。以色列需要根据火灾规模和各条战线造成的损失来调整其反应</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-threat-on-israel-currently-outweighs-irans/00000191-2405-dc0c-a395-ae376d8d0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名巴勒斯坦囚犯的证词描述了加沙战争期间以色列监狱的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-testimonies-from-palestinians-describe-israeli-jails-conditions-during-gaza-war/00000191-238f-d825-abd9-afaf1a3b0000</link><description>以色列-巴勒斯坦非政府组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 的一份新报告披露了自加沙战争开始以来被以色列拘留的数十名巴勒斯坦人的证词。大多数人未经起诉就被释放，他们的叙述详细描述了日常虐待、饥饿、羞辱、剥夺睡眠和拒绝医疗的情况</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-testimonies-from-palestinians-describe-israeli-jails-conditions-during-gaza-war/00000191-238f-d825-abd9-afaf1a3b0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列准备进行报复时，伊朗到底发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-05/ty-article-podcast/what-is-really-going-on-in-iran-while-israel-braces-for-retaliation/00000191-2363-d522-a9df-7f6be5e00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:16:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-05/ty-article-podcast/what-is-really-going-on-in-iran-while-israel-braces-for-retaliation/00000191-2363-d522-a9df-7f6be5e00000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现九名工作人员可能参与了 10 月 7 日对以色列的袭击，联合国解雇了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/un-fires-9-staffers-after-probe-finds-possible-involvement-in-oct-7-attack-on-israel/00000191-23c1-dcd6-abf7-77c727160000</link><description>联合国秘书长办公室在一份简短声明中宣布了这一举措，但没有详细说明近东救济工程处工作人员在袭击中可能扮演的角色；联合国监督机构表示，它在与以色列当局的讨论中借鉴了以色列提供的证据</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 18:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/un-fires-9-staffers-after-probe-finds-possible-involvement-in-oct-7-attack-on-israel/00000191-23c1-dcd6-abf7-77c727160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 304 天：10 月 7 日，九名近东救济工程处工作人员因可能参与其中而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-304-nine-unrwa-workers-fired-for-possible-involvement-in-october-7/00000191-234a-dcd6-abf7-774f440f0001</link><description>西方高级外交官估计，伊朗将在 24 至 48 小时内对哈尼亚在德黑兰的事件做出回应 ■ 伊朗表示无意升级地区紧张局势，但认为需要惩罚以色列 ■ 俄罗斯安全会议秘书正在德黑兰与伊朗领导人会面 ■土耳其表示打算在国际法院正式加入南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案 ■ 这是战争开始 304 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-304-nine-unrwa-workers-fired-for-possible-involvement-in-october-7/00000191-234a-dcd6-abf7-774f440f0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇：让加沙人“饿死”也许是道德的，但世界不会让我们这么做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-starving-gazans-to-death-may-be-moral-but-world-wont-let-us/00000191-22e1-dd23-a7dd-2aed4b050000</link><description>这位极右翼部长在一次右翼会议上表示，目前与哈马斯达成协议的提议“只会遣返少数俘虏，并决定他们中大多数人的命运”</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-starving-gazans-to-death-may-be-moral-but-world-wont-let-us/00000191-22e1-dd23-a7dd-2aed4b050000</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，以色列股市因伊朗罢工威胁而下跌，全球暴跌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/israeli-stocks-fall-amid-threat-of-iran-strike-global-plunge-bloomberg-reports/00000191-22da-dd23-a7dd-2ade679c0000</link><description>特拉维夫主要股指周一上午下跌 2.5%，但随着以色列准备应对伊朗上周两起暗杀事件，下午似乎有所回升</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:08:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/israeli-stocks-fall-amid-threat-of-iran-strike-global-plunge-bloomberg-reports/00000191-22da-dd23-a7dd-2ade679c0000</guid></item><item><title>寻找带有危险基因突变的爱情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-08-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/looking-for-love-with-a-dangerous-gene-mutation/00000191-1c54-d68e-a79b-5fd53a290000</link><description>对于携带 BRCA 基因突变的以色列年轻单身人士来说，尽早做出的决定可以挽救生命。但在一个崇尚生育的国家，以及一个“女性的性取向仍然在很大程度上取决于胸部大小”的社会，人际关系中的困境和不安全感使问题变得复杂</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-08-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/looking-for-love-with-a-dangerous-gene-mutation/00000191-1c54-d68e-a79b-5fd53a290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察因在足球比赛斗殴中袭击国土报记者而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-officer-indicted-for-assaulting-haaretz-journalist-at-soccer-match-brawl/00000191-22c2-d522-a9df-7eeb01640000</link><description>去年一月，一名警察在耶路撒冷泰迪体育场外殴打一名粉丝，并掐死《国土报》作家哈伊姆·莱文森 (Chaim Levinson)，该警官周日面临向法庭提交的袭击指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-officer-indicted-for-assaulting-haaretz-journalist-at-soccer-match-brawl/00000191-22c2-d522-a9df-7eeb01640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有外交政策，只有愿意纵火该地区的总理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-has-no-foreign-policy-only-a-prime-minister-willing-to-set-the-region-ablaze/00000191-2258-d917-a7d5-ff7de7950000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理似乎有意并愿意将以色列夷为平地，因为他认为自己是一个国家的化身，没有他，这个国家就没有生存能力或机构。美国人真的花了30年才意识到这一点吗？</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-has-no-foreign-policy-only-a-prime-minister-willing-to-set-the-region-ablaze/00000191-2258-d917-a7d5-ff7de7950000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官预计伊朗将在未来 24 至 48 小时内对以色列进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-say-iranian-response-expected-within-24-48-hours/00000191-2206-da8c-a393-a2f7ad270000</link><description>谈判失败后，安全评估表明伊朗即将做出回应。关键问题是伊朗报复的强度以及以色列的反应是否会使局势升级为全面战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-say-iranian-response-expected-within-24-48-hours/00000191-2206-da8c-a393-a2f7ad270000</guid></item><item><title>据美国有线电视新闻网报道，尽管经历了十个月的战争，哈马斯在加沙的实力仍在增强</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/hamas-strengthens-in-gaza-despite-ten-months-of-war-cnn-reports/00000191-2251-de46-afd5-f7db10990000</link><description>报道称，只有三个旅被完全摧毁，而哈马斯则合并了退化的组织并招募了新兵。一名加沙人表示，“哈马斯在加沙北部的存在比你想象的要强大，他们就在平民之中”</description><pubDa