ead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</guid></item><item><title>困扰德国的问题塑造了犹太复国主义 — — 并且仍然困扰着以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/problems-that-plagued-germany-shaped-zionism-and-are-still-haunting-israel/00000191-213e-d534-a9f9-6d3fa9500000</link><description>确定当前威胁以色列社会的解体危险的根源</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/problems-that-plagued-germany-shaped-zionism-and-are-still-haunting-israel/00000191-213e-d534-a9f9-6d3fa9500000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派抗议者在以色列中部军事基地外与警察发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-mass-protests-as-summons-date-for-first-1-200-ultra-orthodox-men-looms/00000191-1dca-d534-a9f9-7dcbf7c30000</link><description>以色列军队预计只有大约 30% 的候选人会参加第一天的面试。在极端正统派社区分发的海报呼吁在征兵办公室进行大规模抗议，“我们现在不会为前 1,000 名而战斗，他们会到达我们所有人，但愿不会，包括你的儿子”</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-mass-protests-as-summons-date-for-first-1-200-ultra-orthodox-men-looms/00000191-1dca-d534-a9f9-7dcbf7c30000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗迫在眉睫的威胁将比德黑兰之前的袭击对以色列构成更大的挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-iran-to-attack-military-targets-but-central-israel-is-not-off-limits/00000191-1efd-d68e-a79b-5ffd1a690000</link><description>国防官员预计伊朗和真主党不会收回对以色列暗杀事件进行报复的威胁，以色列可能会面临来自各方的攻击 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡正在拖延时间就人质交易做出决定，美国和以色列官员们越来越沮丧</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-iran-to-attack-military-targets-but-central-israel-is-not-off-limits/00000191-1efd-d68e-a79b-5ffd1a690000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的困境：如何应对以色列暗杀而不自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/irans-dilemma-how-to-respond-to-israels-assassinations-without-committing-suicide/00000191-1f90-d68e-a79b-5f9561330000</link><description>以色列、伊朗和真主党现在陷入了一场屈辱的战争，复仇和威慑的复杂数学很容易被误判并导致全面战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/irans-dilemma-how-to-respond-to-israels-assassinations-without-committing-suicide/00000191-1f90-d68e-a79b-5f9561330000</guid></item></channel></rss>